text: Joanna Kapturska (born Frąckowiak 4 July 1986) is a Polish volleyball player. She plays for AZS KSZO Ostrowiec Świętokrzyski in Poland. She played in the 2012–13 Women's CEV Cup. She is also a member of Poland women's national volleyball team.
